{
  "stem": "14292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jewish organization was established, which was in the center of the Jewish religious center of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it was an organization which is-- had some kind of liaison between the Germans and the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Jews thought, so naively, that by negotiating with the Germans they can able to buy time, or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was-- I understand Eichmann was who sent out some-- two Jewish peasant to Turkey to make some kind of agreement to divest in Jewish leaders in order to buy the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For example, $400 or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they requested trucks, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This--my understanding, these two Hungarians were arrested.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they never had any success, because they considered them some kind of German agent or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so that-- which it's very interesting, as far as, you know, responsibility viewpoint, because it would be possibility to save many people, if they would make that connection.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I can understand why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But on the other hand, you know, when we're talking about responsibilities, this could be a very interesting issue to discuss.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked through this place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think probably in you could see this kind of-- and Schindler goes to these very crowded rooms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That kind of organization I was working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was working in the so-called Contra Division.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Contra Division mean that-- in Budapest, which is obviously the center, and then the country people who is outside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, a very apprehensive man came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And wanted to talk with the leader of the Hungarian-- of the Contra Division.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, his behavior was so peculiar that I wanted to hear what he had to say.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
